dpass - dynamic password prompt
===============================
dpass is an efficient dynamic password prompt for X.


Requirements
------------
In order to build dpass you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (dpass is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install dpass
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running dpass
-------------
See the man page for details.
